> Could always add a new BIP for new wordlists (or perhaps a BIP for the separate WL repo?)

@luke-jr Could you please elaborate on that?

Personally, I am in favour of developing all lists in a separate repo. Not only they are loosely coupled with BTC (or basically any other cryptocurrency - I use my hardware wallet as a second factor and for SSH as well), but also I think BIPs repo would be unnecessarily loaded with PRs and all discussions about it.
